Datasource.Parameter:
(SELECT way, name, ST_Area(way) AS area FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE "natural" IN ('water', 'bay') OR "waterway" IN ('riverbank') ORDER BY z_order ASC, way_area DESC
) AS water
(SELECT way, ST_Area(way) AS area FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE building IS NOT NULL ORDER BY z_order ASC, way_area DESC) AS footprints
